<template>
  {doctors}
  <hello-world />
</template>

<script>
  import axios from 'axios'
  import HelloWorld from '../components/HelloWorld'

  export default {
    name: 'HomeView',
    data () {
      return {
        doctors: null
      }
    },
    async mounted() {
      await this.fetchCatFacts()
    },
    components: {
      HelloWorld,
    },
    methods: {
      async fetchCatFacts() {
        await axios.get('http://localhost:3000/doctors-all').then(response => (this.doctors = response))
      },
      // async loadMoreFacts() {

      //   this.catFacts.push(...(catFactsResponse.data || []))
      //
      //   this.fetchingFacts = false
      // }
    },
  }
</script>
